      "note_no": "2330",
      "note": "The attribution of a son \"begotten\" to Allah has no basis in fact or in reason. It is only a \"word\" or \"saying\" that issues out of their mouths. It is not even a dogma that is reasoned out or can be explained in any way that is consistent with the sublime attributes of Allah. (R)."
